      bash ~/.config/bspwm/scripts/helpers/scratchpad.sh  wclass Org emacs --config org
### News Emacs
hyper + n
      bash ~/.config/bspwm/scripts/helpers/scratchpad.sh  wclass News emacs --config news

### ChatGPT
