### Restart Keybindings sxhkd	    
super + r
      pkill -USR1 -x sxhkd
        
### Restart bspwm
super + shift + r
      pkill -f panel; bspc wm -r

### Restart Panel services
super + shift + b
      bash ~/.config/bspwm/scripts/helpers/bar.sh

